.content

  .col
    %p
      Only 2% of open source contributors are women. Yet open source is the foundation on which the Internet is built, and will only become more important in the future. And it's critical that we hear from diverse voices and engage people with different experiences, talents, and viewpoints as we move forward.

    %p
      Together we can make this happen. This site aims to be a resource for connecting all women of all skill levels to open source projects that are
      =link_to "welcoming, inclusive, and appreciative of diversity", "http://contributor-covenant.org"
      in their contributors.

    %p
      If you have an idea on how to make this site work for you, please submit an issue to
      = succeed "," do
        = link_to "our Github repository", "https://github.com/coralineada/opensourceforwomen.org/"
      or send an email to ideas@opensourceforwomen.org. We also welcome contributions in the form of pull requests.

  .col

    = render 'shared/sign_up_form'
